rComments: I can not emphasize enough how amazing this man is. I've never had such a wonderful experience in a course before encountering him. Funny, engaging, beyond brilliant. Just an all around great man who has something smart to say.Although his classes are at weird times it is well worth it. Will be taking more of his classes in the future.

I had Dr. Bruce every year for something or other. He is an incredibly friendly approachable professor who genuinely cares about his students. Playwriting was one of the best classes I ever took. The only thing that is frustrating about his classes is that he frequently puts off defining the purpose of the course to allow students to do it themselv
